cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "pisinger-knapsack"
abstract: >-
  A deterministic generator of 0/1 knapsack problem instances based on
  Pisinger's scheme, with three value-weight correlation classes, explicit
  seeding, canonical JSON output and a dataset manifest with checksums.
type: software
authors:
